snippet.title: Five Secrets Gameplay
snippet.description: A gamejam game! A gentle afternoon ritual, summoning your grandmother who passed away some years ago. If you can figure out the four rules, you can see her one more time. Each object carries its own significance, both to you personally, and to the summoning ritual.
